'''Michael Prabawa Mohede''' (November 7, 1983 – July 31, 2016),<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://showbiz.liputan6.com/read/2565722/penyanyi-mike-mohede-meninggal-dunia|title=Penyanyi Mike Mohede Meninggal Dunia|last=Ferdian|first=Feby|date=31 July 2016|website=Liputan6.com|publisher=|access-date=2016-07-31}}</ref> better known as '''Mike''', was an [[Indonesia]]n singer and the winner of the [[Indonesian Idol (season 2)|second season]] of ''[[Indonesian Idol]]''. He represented Indonesia in ''[[Asian Idol]]'', losing to [[Hady Mirza]] of ''[[Singapore Idol]]''.
