==Death== Mike died on July 31, 2016 at RS Premier Bintaro (Bintaro Premier Hospital) in [[South Tangerang]], Indonesia from a [[heart attack]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.pikiran-rakyat.com/hidup-gaya/2016/07/31/mike-mohede-meninggal-karena-serangan-jantung-376193|title=Mike Mohede Meninggal Karena Serangan Jantung|last=Yudiawan|first=Deni|date=July 31, 2016|website=Pikiran Rakyat|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://celebrity.okezone.com/read/2016/07/31/33/1451438/mike-mohede-meninggal-rini-sempat-bingung-dengar-kabar-mike|title=Mike Mohede Meninggal: Rini Sempat Bingung dengar Kabar Mike|last=Florencia|first=Menda Clara|date=31 July 2016|website=celebrity.okezone.com|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-01}}</ref> He was 32.<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tribunnews.com/seleb/2016/07/31/mike-mohede-indonesian-idol-dikabarkan-meninggal-dunia|title=Mike Mohede 'Indonesian Idol' Dikabarkan Meninggal Dunia|last=|first=|date=31 July 2016|website=Tribunnews.com|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-01}}</ref><ref>[http://www.thejakartapost.com/life/2016/08/01/singer-michael-mike-mohede-passes-away-at-32.html Singer Michael 'Mike' Mohede passes away at 32]</ref>
